features: 【Food Grade Silicone】 Air fryer silicone basket are non-stick, BPA free, FDA and RoHS compliant, and better than disposable parchment paper liners, making you more inclined to use your air fryer to enjoy healthy food.

【Thickened Design & High Temperature Resistance】 kitCom air fryer silicone liners inserts get 2mm thicker and will not get soft and deformed during baking. Food-grade silicone that can handle up to 453°F/231°C for air frying, steaming, and oven baking.

【The 3d Convex Design On The Bottom】 The heated air is circulated through the bottom of the silicone pots and the sides are slotted to speed up the circulation of heat in the fryer, so that the temperature inside the fryer is evenly distributed and all parts of the food ripen at an identical time.
【Completely Dishwasher Safe】The bottom is designed with a protrusion, which can effectively avoid the sticky and burning residue produced by the food at the bottom during air frying.

【Perfect For All 3-5qt Air Fryers】This air fryer oven accessory can also be used in a steamer, instant pot, microwave and oven, and our air fryer silicone liners are reusable, saving on parchment paper and replacement air fryer baskets.
